miez nucă (0.89%), zahăr vanilinat (1.02%), esență de rom (1.02%), cacao (9.52%), praf de copt (1.02%), ouă (29.94%), sare (0.25%)', 'walnut-and-cocoa-marble-cake', 'walnut-and-cocoa-marble-cake') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
